{"tid":651274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教聯黃均瑜：我那個年代，無讀過通識那些，是『鵪鶉』些、較害怕，現在學生自我張揚，挑戰權威","createTime":"2018-05-03T03:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T04:48:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3037a4c5d883759f6fa6ac4d72a84df7eb165e","tid":651274,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180503/s00001/654f0726e11a8b0c12dd0403d5e2e550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180503%2Fs00001%2F654f0726e11a8b0c12dd0403d5e2e550.jpg&h=ac7caac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府新成立的學校課程檢討專責小組，討論通識教育科（通識科）發展方向，有報道指檢討方向包括文憑試評級改為只有及格或不及格、剔出核心科目或只修不考等。教聯會會長黃均瑜認為檢討合理。<br />\n<br />\n黃均瑜於商台節目表示，通識科爭議不斷，坊間、業界、傳媒都有很多意見，「一直有壓力、要求要檢討」，而到現在推行將近10年，「一個課程十年都要檢討一下」，故認為微調及變更合理。他又說，可以開放檢討毋須設限，最後則要公開諮詢，惟他強調，改變對學生及教師影響大，故大調整須慎重。<br />\n<br />\n問到改變理由，黃均瑜說，通識科是新科目，如果「完全另類」，較難取得別人承認，「如果話考了7、8年，通識科已建立了，可以考慮（檢討）。特別通識科及格率根本已經百分之九十幾，再去分，其實是上面分之嘛&hellip;&hellip;壓力在5*5**那些」。<br />\n<br />\n黃均瑜另提到，「作為中學生，17、8歲，反叛比較強，自己人生經歷不多，給太多批判工具予他，任何事一過了龍就出問題了」，直言他從頭到尾都反對初中便教通識，「這個不行的嘛，修身齊家，學生來說以學為主，搞好自己先，才去看人、批判人」。<br />\n<br />\n黃均瑜又自言，「我那個年代，無讀過通識那些，是『鵪鶉』些、較害怕，現在學生自我張揚，挑戰權威&hellip;&hellip;新高中培養出來的學生，是有這特點的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180503/s00001/1525311307195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180503%2Fs00001%2F1525311307195&d=aAR8aiKAwRVGqn2TrRjSNwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4e6964e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180503%2Fs00001%2F1525311307195&h=72e466a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180503/s00001/1525311307195</a>"},{"pid":"9886981402b1f092219ea296343a3ea6d787950f","tid":651274,"uid":11001,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"做奴才做到咁自豪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2a64751465579b837aba37254936fb40a566ba","tid":651274,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce51e7566e4d575b19980853be5839350f01a481","tid":651274,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"一班心術不正嘅奶共渣滓叫修身齊家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727ed9840595050d3dd820dc68c9329ec64aa7f4","tid":651274,"uid":19557,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 我大學prof 係主張學生挑戰佢 因為prof 都可能會錯"},{"pid":"d395a0733a1080871459a1643113827a1d8e38d5","tid":651274,"uid":118823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"講道理唔夠學生講就用權威黎撻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab150fcc21bc2fe1c2c81a22e9dd28dd4cb54c48","tid":651274,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"所以中國人永遠發展唔<br />\n<br />\n唔挑戰何來進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e36458c5fd1710ebe2d18c099fb772dd99202c","tid":651274,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d1d3734ef4769c9d0746078a8133e8c7b845a2","tid":651274,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"9f8a3b39e6f6d6d58074dd83528fa31d43aae65c","tid":651274,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img s